{"title":"古潜山行","authors":["朔望"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":10,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"古潜山行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朔望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月中旬，随一些老作家访问华北油田一天半。走马观花，匆匆成此，只是引玉的意思。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此石不顽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱说古潜山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峋嶙只不顽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虚涵千味烃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一啸载恩还。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任丘油田按地质构造称“古"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潜山”油田，即由深藏地底的远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古山峰形成。石油是由多种“烃”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天然气自燃不息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱说古潜山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘年十万万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沸情终泄得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一炬识丹丹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋趣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才剥老玉米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青纱帐又起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平原秋趣外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"足下油百里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖畔钻井"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雁翎武工队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菱荇水上庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝何处是？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火种出芦荡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相见欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得意功勋花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗首井家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非无困窘日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细玩八粒沙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年打第一口井（今称功勋井）时，初觉无功，忽从岩浆中发现八颗含石油的沙粒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国际友谊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六千米深钻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高悬罗国名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隆隆日夕意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尺寸俱有情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采油小院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一刻抵万金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔油侧耳听。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却从闲令节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辟得几畦青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种的萝卜、青菜、白薯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起我沉山梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴我震旦魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心窗不耐暝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯火近红门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国古称震旦。震旦纪为元古代岩层名，古潜山属之。北京南苑有大红门。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}